# General
- Use TypeScript everywhere.
- Use clear, minimal, production-ready code.
- Use proper file/folder structure automatically, donâ€™t dump everything in one file.

# Backend (Express + MongoDB)
- Folder: backend/
- Use Express with TypeScript.
- Use Mongoose for MongoDB.
- Create models: User, Form, Submission.
- Use JWT for authentication.
- Store Cloudinary file URLs, not raw files.
- Create utils for db connection, gemini integration, cloudinary.

# Frontend (Next.js 15 + TypeScript + Tailwind)
- Folder: frontend/
- Use App Router.
- Pages: login, signup, dashboard, form/[id].
- Components: FormRenderer, Navbar, FormCard.
- Use react-hook-form for handling forms.
- Axios for API calls, attach JWT in headers.

# AI
- Integrate Google Gemini API.
- Always return a JSON schema for form fields.

# Style/UI
- Use TailwindCSS for styling.
- Clean, modern UI with responsive design.